&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PRODUCT APPLICATIONS MANAGER - WATER TREATEMENT&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The primary purpose of this position is to lead the wastewater technical service function—partnering closely with Water and Manufactured Solutions sales teams to deliver expert support, drive new business growth, and protect existing accounts. The position plays a key role in advancing Hydrite’s vision to be the most trusted, respected, and sought-after provider of solutions that ensure customer success.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Primary responsibilities include:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
